<div class="about-header">
  <h1>About Our Restaurant</h1>
  <p>Learn more about our story, values, and commitment to great food</p>
</div>
<div class="about-content">
  <div class="about-section">
    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>
      Founded in 2020, our restaurant began as a small family dream to bring
      authentic, delicious food to our community. What started as a passion
      project has grown into a beloved local establishment where friends and
      families gather to share memorable meals.
</p> <p>
      Our founders, Maria and Giuseppe, immigrated from Italy with nothing
but
      their grandmother's recipes and an unwavering commitment to quality.
      Today, we continue to honor those traditions while embracing modern
culinary techniques and local ingredients.
    </p>
</div>
  <div class="about-section">
    <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
    <p>
      We believe that great food brings people together. Every dish we serve
      is prepared with care, using fresh, locally-sourced ingredients
whenever
      possible. Our chefs combine traditional techniques with creative flair
      to create dishes that are both familiar and exciting.
    </p>
    <p>
      Sustainability is important to us. We work with local farmers and
      suppliers to reduce our environmental impact while supporting our
      community. Our menu changes seasonally to reflect the best ingredients
      available.
</p> </div>
  <div class="about-section">
    <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
    <div class="team-grid">
      <div class="team-member">
        <h3>Maria Rodriguez</h3>
        <p><strong>Head Chef & Co-Owner</strong></p>
        <p>With 15 years of culinary experience, Maria leads our kitchen with
passion and precision.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="team-member">
        <h3>Giuseppe Martinez</h3>
        <p><strong>Restaurant Manager & Co-Owner</strong></p>
        <p>Giuseppe ensures every guest has an exceptional dining experience
from start to finish.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="team-member">
        <h3>Sarah Johnson</h3>
        <p><strong>Sous Chef</strong></p>
        <p>Sarah brings creativity and innovation to our menu while
maintaining our high standards.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="about-section">
    <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
    <p>Have questions or feedback? We'd love to hear from you!</p>
    <%= form_with url: contact_path, local: true, class: "contact-form" do
|form| %>
      <div class="form-group">
        <%= form.label :name, "Your Name" %>
        <%= form.text_field :name, class: "form-control", required: true %>
</div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <%= form.label :email, "Your Email" %>
        <%= form.email_field :email, class: "form-control", required: true %>
</div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <%= form.label :message, "Your Message" %>
        <%= form.text_area :message, class: "form-control", rows: 4,
required: true %>
      </div>
      <%= form.submit "Send Message", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
